| filter $p.app_name == null || $p.app_name.arrayContains(cx_rum.version_metadata.app_name)
| filter $p.device == null || $p.device.arrayContains(cx_rum.session_context.device) 
| filter $p.country_name == null || $p.country_name.arrayContains(cx_rum.session_context.ip_geoip.country_name)   
| filter $p.app_version == null ||  $p.app_version.arrayContains(cx_rum.version_metadata.app_version)
| filter $p.browser == null ||  $p.browser.arrayContains(cx_rum.session_context.browser)
| filter $p.session_id == null || $p.session_id.arrayContains(cx_rum.session_context.session_id)
| filter cx_rum.resource_context !=null
| create dns_duration from cx_rum.resource_context.domainLookupEnd
 - cx_rum.resource_context.domainLookupStart
| groupby cx_rum.resource_context.fragments as fragments, $m.timestamp/5m agg avg(dns_duration:num)
